OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FWes Streeting has pressed the
OL,7,FGovernment to bring in the
OL,8,FHillsborough law before the summer to
OL,9,Fimprove NHS maternity services.
OL,11,FThe former health secretary said
OL,12,Fculture change in maternity care will
OL,13,Fnot happen without proper
OL,14,Faccountability.
OL,16,FMr Streeting called for the propsoed
OL,17,FHillsborough Law to be implemented
OL,18,Fbefore the House of Commons rises for
OL,19,Fthe summer, saying its duty of candour
OL,20,Frules will help end the "cover-up
OL,21,Fculture" in the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FHis comments follow a new report from
OL,7,FBaroness Valerie Amos, which calls for
OL,8,Furgent action on maternity and a need
OL,9,Fto listen to women and families.
OL,11,FIt also comes in the wake of Donna
OL,12,FOckenden's inquiry into maternity
OL,13,Fservices at Nottingham University
OL,14,FHospitals NHS Trust, which found more
OL,15,Fthan 500 mothers and babies suffered
OL,16,Fpotentially avoidable harm or death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FAddressing the Commons on Tuesday 30
OL,7,FJune, Mr Streeting said: "Of all of
OL,8,Fthe conversations I had with families
OL,9,Fwho were suffering bereavement or harm
OL,10,Ffor themselves or for their children,
OL,11,Fthe thing that shocked me most is the
OL,12,Fcover-up culture in the NHS, which
OL,13,Fcontinues to persist to this day."
OL,15,FHe said there was a legitimate debate
OL,16,Fto be had on whether a full statutory
OL,17,Fpublic inquiry was needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FHe added: "Whatever the answer to that
OL,7,Fquestion is, it's only worth the paper
OL,8,Fit's written on if all of those
OL,9,Finvolved in decision-making and care
OL,10,Fare held to account with a duty of
OL,11,Fcandour.
OL,13,F"Given that, where is the Hillsborough
OL,14,Flaw? Because it's important not just
OL,15,Ffor justice for the 97 but also for
OL,16,Fthese families and to prevent future
OL,17,Fharms, will that law at least go
OL,18,Fthrough this House before the summer
OL,19,Frecess, because until it's on the
OL,20,Fbooks, people continue to duck
OL,21,Fanswering real questions?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FJames Murray, who replaced Mr
OL,7,FStreeting as Health Secretary, agreed
OL,8,Fthat the "culture of cover-ups" would
OL,9,Fcontinue without proper accountability.
OL,11,F"Senior clinicians will feel they can
OL,12,Fcontinue to get away with mistakes
OL,13,Fwhen they happen, senior clinicians
OL,14,Fwill feel they can avoid scrutiny when
OL,15,Finvestigations take place and they
OL,16,Fwill fundamentally continue, in too
OL,17,Fmany cases, to be more concerned with
OL,18,Fprotecting themselves than protecting
OL,19,Fwomen and babies."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FHe added: "I think the duty of candour
OL,7,Fis the one single most powerful change
OL,8,Fwe can make clearly, loudly, publicly,
OL,9,Fbecause the message it will send to
OL,10,Fsenior clinicians thinking about what
OL,11,Fto do in the future if they make a
OL,12,Fmistake or if they are tempted to
OL,13,Fcover up things that go wrong in the
OL,14,Ffuture is that one day they will be
OL,15,Fheld to account.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,F"With a duty and candour in place,
OL,7,Fthere will no longer be an opportunity
OL,8,Ffor clinicians to refuse to engage in
OL,9,Fthat process, to refuse to be held to
OL,10,Faccount, be part of the justice
OL,11,Fprocess, people will face up to two
OL,12,Fyears in prison if they refuse to
OL,13,Fcooperate."
OL,15,FWhile he agreed on the importance of
OL,16,Fthe draft legislation, he offered no
OL,17,Fpromises the Hillsborough Law would be
OL,18,Fin place before the summer recess.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FThe draft legislation, formally known
OL,7,Fas the Public Office (Accountability)
OL,8,FBill, was carried over from the last
OL,9,Fparliamentary session.
OL,11,FIt will require public officials to
OL,12,Ftell the truth during inquiries and
OL,13,Finvestigations, and was promised by
OL,14,FLabour in its 2024 manifesto.
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer previously pledged to
OL,17,Fdeliver the draft law by April 15 last
OL,18,Fyear, to mark the 36th anniversary of
OL,19,Fthe disaster where 97 Liverpool
OL,20,Ffootball fans were unlawfully killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FHowever, progress was stalled
OL,7,Ffollowing concerns over changes which
OL,8,Fcould see the proposed duty of candour
OL,9,Fnot applied to intelligence agencies.
OL,11,FSir Jeremy Hunt, another former health
OL,12,Fsecretary, said he agreed with Mr
OL,13,FStreeting.
OL,15,FThe Conservative MP said regulations
OL,16,Fto "make it a criminal offence for
OL,17,F(NHS) trusts not to tell the truth"
OL,18,Fwere passed during his time at the
OL,19,FDepartment of Health and Social Care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,F"Yet to this day, trust lawyers advise
OL,7,Fdoctors, nurses and midwives not to be
OL,8,Fopen about what's happened when there
OL,9,Fis a prospect of legal action further
OL,10,Fdown the line," Sir Jeremy added.
OL,12,FTurning to Mr Murray, Sir Jeremy
OL,13,Fasked: "Will he agree that in the
OL,14,FHillsborough Law, we will clear up
OL,15,Fthis anomaly so that it is just not
OL,16,Fpossible for trusts not to tell the
OL,17,Ftruth, and trust lawyers always advise
OL,18,Ftheir own doctors, nurses and midwives
OL,19,Fthey must tell families exactly what
OL,20,Fhappened?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782907570
OL,3,CHillsborough Law needed to tackle NHS
OL,4,C'cover-up culture' says Wes Streeting
OL,6,FThe minister vowed to "look into" the
OL,7,Fpoint Sir Jeremy raised.
OL,9,F"That does sound concerning," he
OL,10,Fcontinued.
OL,12,FMr Murray said he "couldn't quite
OL,13,Fbelieve" how many senior clinicians
OL,14,Frefused to take part in the previous
OL,15,Freview by Ms Ockenden of maternity
OL,16,Fcare in Nottingham.
OL,18,F"It is unacceptable that so many
OL,19,Fsenior clinicians were able to and
OL,20,Ffelt able to just say 'no'," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
